{
  "texts": [
    "The confidence cost in the absence of an object is described by the notation \" notar \" in Eq. 5.",
    "The confidence in the truth and prediction are denoted by C i and Ci.",
    "In Eq. 6, the term \"classification error\" is used to describe the accuracy of categorization.",
    "(5) The discovered target's class is denoted by the letter c in Eq. 6.",
    "The genuine probability that the target is in class c is denoted by the p i (c) symbol."
  ]
}